description: With a dream to lead a sweet career, the perfect plan popped into Chef Erin’s head: take the best, freshest, locally-grown organic ingredients, and concoct the tastiest frozen creations. Many fruity experiments and a few years later, Erin’s own Front Porch Pops shops & carts are now the coolest and most popular popsicle spots in Santa Ana. You’ll find a delightful variety of Fruity, Creamy, or Creamsicle (fifty-fifty) flavors that range from sweetly nostalgic, like Hawaiian Punch, Root Beer Float, and Strawberries N’ Cream, to deliciously innovative, like Lemon Raspberry Cheesecake, Roasted Peach Raspberry, or Balsamic Strawberry Swirl. There's much more too, and as you can probably tell, it all tastes so awesome. So stop on by Front Porch Pops and get your happiness on a stick fix soon. And if you’re planning a hoppin’ party or event, this scrumptious selection of treats is sure to please your every guest.
name: Front Porch Pops
